STATE of Washington, Respondent,
v.
Christopher Von Keith COWAN, Petitioner. No. 95866-1 Supreme Court of Washington. DATED at Olympia, Washington this 1st day of November, 2018.

ORDER

¶ 1 This matter came before the Court on its November 1, 2018, En Banc Conference. The Court considered the petition and the files herein. A majority of the Court voted in favor of the following result:

¶ 2 Now, therefore, it is hereby

¶ 3 ORDERED:

¶ 4 That the petition for review is denied.

For the Court

/s/ Fairhurst, C.J.

CHIEF JUSTICE
